Package: devaultd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Wallet Daemon.
 Desktop Wallet for DeVault, a decentralized cryptocurrency.
 .
 This package provides the daemon, devaultd, and the CLI tool
 devault-cli to interact with the daemon.

Package: devault-qt
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Wallet GUI.
 Desktop Wallet for DeVault, a decentralized cryptocurrency.
 .
 This package provides devault-qt, a GUI for DeVault based on Qt.

Package: devault-tx
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: DeVault TX.
 Desktop Wallet for DeVault, a decentralized cryptocurrency.
 .
 This package provides devault-tx, a command-line transaction creation
 tool which can be used without a bitcoin daemon.  Some means of
 exchanging minimal transaction data with peers is still required.
